                        exit
                    exit

                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 733 create

#--------------------------------------------------
echo "Policy Configuration"
#--------------------------------------------------
        policy-options
            begin
            prefix-list "plHostRoute"
                prefix 0.0.0.0/0 prefix-length-range 32-32
            exit
            prefix-list "plLinkLocalv6"
                prefix fe80::/10 exact
                prefix fec0::/10 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "plLoopLocalv6"
                prefix ::1/128 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "plDefaultRoute"
                prefix 0.0.0.0/0 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "plPrivateRoute"
                prefix 10.0.0.0/8 exact
                prefix 10.0.0.0/8 longer
                prefix 172.16.0.0/12 exact
                prefix 172.16.0.0/12 longer
                prefix 192.168.0.0/16 exact
                prefix 192.168.0.0/16 longer
            exit
            community "cmNBMAN" members "64741:1503" "64741:12052"
            community "target:4134:647411108" members "target:4134:647411108"
            community "target:4134:647411303" members "target:4134:647411303"
            policy-statement "rpFROMCR_INv6"
                entry 10
                    from
                        protocol bgp
                        prefix-list "plDefaultRoutev6"
                    exit
                    action accept
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            policy-statement "rpSET_COMM_OUT"
                entry 10
                    from
                        prefix-list "plDefaultRoute"
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action reject
                exit
                entry 20
                    from
                        prefix-list "plPrivateRoute"
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action reject
                exit
                entry 30
                    from
                        protocol direct
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action accept
                        community replace "cmNBMAN "
                    exit
                exit
                entry 40
                    from
                        protocol static
                        tag 100
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action accept
                        community replace "cmNBMAN "
                        next-hop-self
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            policy-statement "rpStaticToBGPv6"
                entry 10
                    from
                        tag 100
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action accept
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            policy-statement "rpLDPLabelFilter"
                entry 10
                    from
                        prefix-list "plHostRoute"
                    exit
                    action accept
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            policy-statement "rpSET_COMM_OUTv6"
                entry 10
                    from
                        prefix-list "plDefaultRoutev6"
                    exit
                    to
                        protocol bgp
                    exit
                    action reject
                exit
                entry 20
                    from

                    exit

                    exit

            commit
